    "text": "Fitness is a mental game."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.929,
    "endTime": 5.9,
    "text": "And regret is that inner demon we all share."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.504,
    "endTime": 9.975,
    "text": "You can think about what you should do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.834,
