    "text": "You can think about what you could do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.39,
    "endTime": 18.071,
    "text": "You can think about what you would have done,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.299,
    "endTime": 20.0,
    "text": "but your body won't go"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.001,
    "endTime": 22.166,
    "text": "where your mind won't push it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.675,
    "endTime": 45.644999999999996,
    "text": "Change your mental vocabulary."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.939,
    "endTime": 48.159,
    "text": "Join the present."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.154,
    "endTime": 53.524,
